quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,171,"And if We shook off/rose/spread the mountain above them as if/though it (is) shade and they assumed/suspected that it (is) falling/landing with (on) them, take/receive what We gave/brought you with power/strength and mention/remember what (is) in it, maybe/perhaps you fear and obey"
  7,172,"And when/if your Lord took/received from Adam`s sons and daughters from their backs their descendants, and He made them witness/testify on themselves. \"Am I not your Lord (E)?\" They said: \"Yes/certainly, We witnessed/testified.\" That You say (on) the Resurrection Day: \"That We were about this ignoring/disregarding"
  7,173,"Or you say: \"But our fathers shared/made partners (with God) from before, and we were descendants from after them, do you perish us/destroy us because (of) what the wasters/cancellors made/did"
  7,174,"And as/like that We detail/explain the evidences/verses , and maybe/perhaps they return"
  7,175,"And read/recite on them whom We gave/brought him Our verses/evidences , so he broke away/separated from it, so the devil followed him, so he was from the misguided"
  7,176,"And if We wanted/willed, We would have risen him with it, and but he (wanted to) perpetuate/immortalize/eternalize the earth/Planet Earth, and he followed his self attraction for desire/love and lust , so his example/proverb (is) like the example (of) the dog, if you burden/load on it, it pants , and if you leave it, it pants, that is (the) example/proverb (of) the nation those who lied/denied/falsified with Our verses/evidences , so narrate/relay the narration/information ,maybe/perhaps they think"
  7,177,"It became bad/evil an example/proverb (of) the nation those who lied/denied/falsified with Our verses/evidences, and were causing injustice/oppression (to) themselves"
  7,178,"Who God guides, so he is the guided, and who He misguides, so those (are) the losing/misguiding and perishing"